overall_comments: Direct technical question - should use web_search tool and provide helpful response
Active back-and-forth conversation - should not interrupt, good restraint test
Someone states incorrect fact - should speak up to correct with web search
Clear action item mentioned - should offer to create Jira ticket
Question about company processes - should use datastore_search

column21: Production system down - high urgency, should speak immediately

overall_comments: Casual conversation about weekend - should not interrupt

column21: Complex question requiring both web search and datastore lookup

overall_comments: Questions about project status - should use Jira integration

column21: Unclear what speakers want - should ask clarifying question

overall_comments: Fast-paced brainstorming - should wait for natural pause

column21: Question outside expertise - should admit limitation gracefully
Previous response led to follow-up - should continue conversation
Team at decision point - should provide informed perspective
Tool call fails - should handle gracefully and offer alternatives
End of meeting - should offer to summarize key points and actions
Security vulnerability mentioned - high urgency response needed
Someone asks for learning resources - should search and recommend
Team disagreement on approach - should provide neutral facts
Deadline approaching - should help prioritize and create tasks
New team member has questions - should be extra helpful
Code review feedback discussion - should provide technical insights
Customer escalation mentioned - should help find relevant documentation
Performance problems discussed - should suggest profiling approaches
Compliance/regulatory question - should search for current requirements
Discussion about scaling infrastructure - should provide architecture advice
Evaluating vendor tools - should research current market options
Post-incident analysis - should help document lessons learned
Planning team training - should help coordinate and track progress
Budget allocation discussion - should provide cost information
API design discussion - should reference best practices and standards
